e of the garland on its head has a relaxing effect. It withers if a Trainer does not take good care of it."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Even veteran Trainers face a challenge in getting its beautiful flower to bloom. This Pok\u00e9mon is popular with celebrities."},{"version":"sun","text":"No matter how much time and money is spent raising it, its flowers are the most beautiful when they bloom in the wild."},{"version":"moon","text":"As soon as it finds a male to be its partner, the beautiful flower on its head darkens, droops, and withers away."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"The fragrance of its flower differs slightly depending on the soil where it grew up. Sniffing the aroma calms your heart and mind."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It\u2019s well liked by other Pok\u00e9mon because of its beauty. The flower on its head needs constant care, or it will soon wither and rot."},{"version":"sword","text":"It\u2019s believed that even first-rate gardeners have a hard time getting the flower on a Lilligant\u2019s head to bloom."},{"version":"shield","text":"Essential oils made from Lilligant flowers have a sublime scent, but they\u2019re also staggeringly expensive."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"I suspect that its well-developed legs are the result of a life spent on mountains covered in deep snow. The scent it exudes from its flower crown heartens those in proximity."}],"evo":{"name":"petilil","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"lilligant","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"sun-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":fals